This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image processing and enhancement techniques. The use of a fully-convolutional network for end-to-end training also suggests a machine learning (cs.MM) sub-category. The paper also discusses factors that affect performance, which could fall under the machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the dataset creation and analysis could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category.
